# scope|path|direction|name|reason
command|root|local-only|help|container-compose exposes an explicit help command through Swift ArgumentParser; Docker Compose 5.2.0 standalone supports help flags but does not list help as a root command.
option|root|local-only|--verbose|Accepted by container-compose for existing bug-report and version workflows; Docker Compose 5.2.0 standalone accepts `docker-compose --verbose version` but does not list the flag in root help.
